CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,FA team of specialist firefighters from
OL,7,Fthe North West who have supported the
OL,8,Frescue efforts in earthquake hit
OL,9,FVenezuela are back home.
OL,11,FFirefighters from Merseyside,
OL,12,FLancashire, Cheshire and Greater
OL,13,FManchester have been helping locate
OL,14,Fsurvivors trapped beneath collapsed
OL,15,Fbuildings after two devastating
OL,16,Fearthquakes struck Venezuela last
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
