OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,FThe 68-strong team, made up of
OL,7,Ffirefighters and specialist personnel
OL,8,Ffrom 14 UK fire and rescue services
OL,9,Fwere deployed along with six search
OL,10,Fdogs.
OL,12,FThey also had specialist capabilities
OL,13,Fincluding medical, engineering and
OL,14,Fveterinary support.
OL,16,FThe team took off from RAF Brize
OL,17,FNorton as part of the UK's
OL,18,Fhumanitarian response to the disaster,
OL,19,Fwhich claimed more than 3,500 lives
OL,20,Fand affected millions of people across
OL,21,Fthe country.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,FDuring their deployment, UK ISAR
OL,7,Festablished a Base of Operations in
OL,8,Fthe Venezuelan capital of La Guaira
OL,9,Fwhere they helped coordinate searches
OL,10,Falongside the country's authorities,
OL,11,FUnited Nations agencies and global
OL,12,Fresponse partners.
OL,14,FThe team also conducted street-by-
OL,15,Fstreet assessments of hundreds of
OL,16,Fdamaged buildings, identified hazards
OL,17,Fand humanitarian needs, and helped
OL,18,Fdetermine where further search and
OL,19,Frescue efforts should be focused.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,FThe team's six specialist search dogs
OL,7,Fwere used throughout the operation to
OL,8,Fsupport search efforts and help safely
OL,9,Fclear structures.
OL,11,FUK ISAR personnel also worked
OL,12,Falongside international search and
OL,13,Frescue teams from countries including
OL,14,FChile, the United States, France,
OL,15,FGermany, Spain, Italy, Turkey, Qatar
OL,16,Fand Ecuador as part of a coordinated
OL,17,Fmultinational response.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,FAs the emergency response moved into
OL,7,Fits final stages, UK ISAR coordinated
OL,8,Fthe safe demobilisation and
OL,9,Frepatriation of personnel, dogs and
OL,10,Fspecialist equipment before returning
OL,11,Fto the UK.
OL,13,FChair of the National Fire Chiefs
OL,14,FCouncil (NFCC), Phil Garrigan, said:
OL,15,F"I know the whole of the UK Fire and
OL,16,FRescue Services is incredibly proud of
OL,17,Fthe UK ISAR team and their relentless
OL,18,Fefforts during this deployment.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783678767
OL,3,CSpecialist firefighters looking for
OL,4,Csurvivors in Venezuela return home
OL,6,F"Working in extremely challenging
OL,7,Fconditions, they demonstrated the
OL,8,Fprofessionalism, expertise and
OL,9,Fcompassion that makes the UK's search
OL,10,Fand rescue capability world-class.
OL,12,F"Our thoughts remain with the people
OL,13,Fof Venezuela, so many of whom have
OL,14,Fsuffered unimaginable loss. The team
OL,15,Fhave expressed how the warmth,
OL,16,Fgratitude and welcome shown to them
OL,17,Fthroughout the operation will stay
OL,18,Fwith them for a long time."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
